Second parameter of `map-get` is the key.
`$negative-spacers` (when `$enable-negative-margins` is set to `true`) contains: `("n1": -0.25rem, "n2": -0.5rem, "n3": -1rem, "n4": -1.5rem, "n5": -3rem)`.

So in your case it would rather be `map-get($negative-spacers, n3);` if you need to have `-1rem`. So:
```scss
.whatever {
  margin: map-get($negative-spacers, "n3");
}
```
will result in:
```css
.whatever {
  margin: -1rem;
}
```

